{"tid":2517660,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[町田啓太x赤楚衛二] 如果30歲還是處男，似乎就能成為魔法師 /演員相關討論  59","createTime":"2021-05-05T12:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T15:47:32.000Z","uid":5000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"642dfe14ef3247a74d4247f50b986e9f8a953a07","tid":2517660,"uid":5000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:44:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4R9fAsOLpfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4R9fAsOLpfI&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=5fa7731a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4R9fAsOLpfI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://realsound.jp/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/20200904-cherimaho-main.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frealsound.jp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F20200904-cherimaho-main.jpeg&h=a8a9ec7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豐田悠在pixiv連載中的作品「如果30歲還是處男，似乎就能成為魔法師」真人日劇化；故事講述由於安達（赤楚衛二飾演）30歲了還保有處男之身，因此變得能使用魔法。他得到的是「只要接觸就能讀取人心」這般多餘又樸素的魔法之力。<br />\n這樣的某日，他無意間讀取到工作優秀的同期帥哥同事──黑澤（町田啟太飾演）的心，黑澤的心中，充滿了對安達的無限愛戀!?<br />\n赤楚衛二x町田啟太主演BL漫改電視劇《如果30歲還是處男，似乎就能成為魔法師》，東京電視台10月8日開播<br />\n<br />\n官方twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tx_cherimaho?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftx_cherimaho%3Fs%3D21&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=4c8b2cd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tx_cherimaho?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n町田啓太ig<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/keita_machida_official?igshid=z29dmx3q10b1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fkeita_machida_official%3Figshid%3Dz29dmx3q10b1&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=275fcd38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/keita_machida_official?igshid=z29dmx3q10b1</a><br />\n<br />\n赤楚衛二ig<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/akasoeiji?igshid=etjx3bl1d64v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fakasoeiji%3Figshid%3Detjx3bl1d64v&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=981edf95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/akasoeiji?igshid=etjx3bl1d64v</a><br />\n<br />\nOP - Omoinotake - 産声<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cwC7u-XdpLM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcwC7u-XdpLM&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=67a27cd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cwC7u-XdpLM</a><br />\n<br />\nED - Deep Squad - Good Love Your Love<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2aaUQuXyuCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2aaUQuXyuCA&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=cd26e271\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2aaUQuXyuCA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/12/22/023851_6c5c8f0aea23a6e0e8dba8436a3d444f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F12%2F22%2F023851_6c5c8f0aea23a6e0e8dba8436a3d444f.gif&h=27e52174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">請勿流出加密內容 </span><br />\n維持和平 你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鹹魚青菜 各有所好<br />\n請各位互相尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">請注意！！<br />\n所有收費內容，包括圖，影片，連結等等禁止外傳，貼出時請加密。<br />\n如發現有收費內容流出，會停止分享所有與收費平台有關的資訊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請善用加密/細字功能，切勿濫用四重<br />\n以下情況請用四重加密<br />\n- 劇透<br />\n- 唔可以外傳嘅source/link <br />\n- CLS FF<br />\n- 千字文回覆<br />\n- 圖海<br />\n<br />\nOff topic時可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或<span class=\"small\">細字</span><br />\n希望各位教友遵守<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc7e5861b21cea240f4c56b1ab85e1ddd032da8","tid":2517660,"uid":5000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,